# Technical Stack

- Python for backend
- react for the frontend
- PostgreSQL databases, never JSON file storage
- Separate databeses for dev, test, and prod
- Elasticsearch for search, using elastic.co hosting
- Elastic.co will have dev and prod indexes
- Python tests
- Cloud build:
    - Back-end: AWS Elastic Beanstalk
    - Front-end: S3 Build + CloudFront
    - Database: RDS
    - API REST exposed on API Gateway
    - Application Load Balancer
    - Network: Traditional VPC
